text: Garrett Gray Nash was a male United States international table tennis player. He won a bronze medal at the 1948 World Table Tennis Championships in the men's team event. He was inducted into the USA Table Tennis Hall of Fame in 1991. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:American male table tennis players Category:1997 deaths Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Garrett Nash
